共做得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/jjj_hkong/status/1182935681640751104?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjjj_hkong%2Fstatus%2F1182935681640751104%3Fs%3D21&d=BELmNDq%2B1pqro4agOzjMGYLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=b943f86b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjjj_hkong%2Fstatus%2F1182935681640751104%3Fs%3D21&h=5b09c229\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/jjj_hkong/status/1182935681640751104?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n有無丁點人性啊？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今日香港人話比你聽個情況有無好到！！</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AuFqq0r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAuFqq0r.jpg&h=17ee4a72&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"68f12178b5260fece689aaeaed05e826a774a8d7","tid":1650554,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T04:33:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b2c06d57350ace3394619ea435810a404f4db3b","tid":1650554,"uid":53037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T04:34:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f3d006b7fe1ecaea015924d3bcb1c9d8e565e18","tid":1650554,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T04:36:17.000Z","msg":"有野想捐可以FB搵我地香港自由之書阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face